> –horizontal-pod-autoscaler-initial-readiness-delay (default: 30 seconds)

`--horizontal-pod-autoscaler-initial-readiness-delay` defines a delay right after a pod enters the Ready state. this delay is necessary because sometimes pods can fluctuate between Ready and Unready states initially. so this is an ensurance policy for hpa
